message.body: Have you heard of piccalo? I'm watching bourdain and he's in minneapolis eating there
Mmmmmmmm nope! What kind of food is it?
Fusion i think? Fancy and super pretentious. Looks awesome
Doesn't sound like my scene. $1 tacos please.
I have yet to eat anywhere outside of my home. I wonder what the world is like out there! I just asked my mom for tacos and now she's making them. I want spice!
Hah. Tell her! Tell her to get 'chili'.
